{"tid":955423,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利埃特納火山爆發　引發逾130次地震　部分空域關閉","createTime":"2018-12-25T11:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T15:06:04.000Z","uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be705ac14160ec94a26236f590a92c8265df9311","tid":955423,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:40:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/275142#media_id=2248450_blank\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F275142%23media_id%3D2248450_blank&d=nwIIHGTlHaa4WJpxqbIjP6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=9af20cc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/275142#media_id=2248450_blank</a><br />\n<br />\n意大利西西里島（Sicily）著名活火山&mdash;&mdash;埃特納火山（Mount Etna）周一（24日）爆發，引發逾130次地震，最強達黎克特制4.3級。受火山灰影響，附近機場需要實施空中管制，每小時只允許4班客機降落。暫無傷亡報告。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2248446/org/cf44c876aa9f98743c6444e940924d6a.jpg/3cwLmEFvqaZR2kqIxpf51waZ0ddAKu-NRKre_USq3v0?v=w640r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2248446%2Forg%2Fcf44c876aa9f98743c6444e940924d6a.jpg%2F3cwLmEFvqaZR2kqIxpf51waZ0ddAKu-NRKre_USq3v0%3Fv%3Dw640r16_9&h=8edb2652&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）周二（24日）引述埃特納火山觀測站稱，熔漿從埃特納火山東南部火山口的新裂縫噴湧而出，火山灰覆蓋附近村莊，所幸暫無傷亡報告。<br />\n<br />\n由於火山灰導致附近空域能見度不佳，卡坦尼亞機場（Catania Airport）實施空中管制，每小時只准4班航機降落，機場當地晚上8時將恢復正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n意大利國家地球物理和火山研究所（INGV）火山學家貝恩克（Boris Behncke）表示：「噴發活動發生在埃特納火山的側邊，是十多年來第一次橫向噴發。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2248450/org/fe2d3a98a0e1daeb448247c101b64d7a.JPG/IC01bve6AKvPJjMPfGQXj3mrm6BVEvcfV9RxxlfUccY?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2248450%2Forg%2Ffe2d3a98a0e1daeb448247c101b64d7a.JPG%2FIC01bve6AKvPJjMPfGQXj3mrm6BVEvcfV9RxxlfUccY%3Fv%3Dw640&h=4ed7a9d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7b432c4dac885692ee7f9b5aee1d29986cd8dc1","tid":955423,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:41:00.000Z","msg":"冇死人😂✌🏼"},{"pid":"8214bc7a48f9dca466a29430a7647f0e6d8f5aaf","tid":955423,"uid":89595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:43:39.000Z","msg":"HK01真係世界級垃圾<br />\n火山名都串錯做Etan<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我手動改咗<br />\n譯名就算 維基都係咁譯<br />\n但係Catania我都改咗做卡<span style=\"color: red;\">坦</span>尼亞而唔係卡塔尼亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2d547698d3c5488c1d84cfa668ba5b042617dd","tid":955423,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"其實我係想問<br />\n有冇巴絲嚟緊會去西西里<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce87ed8446aafcb7648df09df1bc72adf9c8ab3","tid":955423,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以quote #2 講咗啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4694e734b351a141bd2c7e4648cfb967fb30f9","tid":955423,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ce87ed8446aafcb7648df09df1bc72adf9c8ab3","tid":955423,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以quote #2 講咗啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"201519c1031757500815fb2839181ad940c0a629","tid":955423,"uid":14459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f4694e734b351a141bd2c7e4648cfb967fb30f9","tid":955423,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ce87ed8446aafcb7648df09df1bc72adf9c8ab3","tid":955423,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以quote #2 講咗啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},"citedBy":1